message: Justin Teeter Bensing, 36, was arrested on Feb. 12 for soliciting an undercover police officer he believed to be a minor.  He drove from his home in Myrtle Beach all the way to Greenville to pick up the 14-year-old he thought he was communicating with.

attachments.media_description: Scary New Details About The Man Who Tried to Lure A 14-Year-Old Child Into Being A 'Full-Time Baby Maker' And Wanted To 'Cannibalize' Her
